LT_REV is the average of the returns on two (big and small) low prior return portfolios
minus the average of the returns on two high prior return portfolios.  The portfolios
are constructed daily.  Big means a firm is above the median market cap on the NYSE
at the end of the previous day; small firms are below the median NYSE market cap.
Prior return is measured from day -1250 to -251.  Firms in the low prior return
